Glimpse S3 method for chronogram objects (class cg_tbl)

Usage

# S3 method for class 'cg_tbl'
glimpse(x, width = NULL, ...)

Arguments

x

a chrongram

width, ...

passed to pillar::glimpse

Value

print to console

Examples

library(dplyr)
data("built_smallstudy")
cg <- built_smallstudy$chronogram
glimpse(cg)
